Class VariableProxy

Variables are synchronized in a 'last-writer-wins' scheme. When the VariableProxy mutates the model, it sets a barrier and expects to receive the barrier value echoed back in a subsequent update event. Between those two points in time updates are not applied or notified about as these reflect concurrent writes that did not 'win'.
